nodes.text: A Twi'lek was the owner and announcer for the famed Circus Horrificus. The circus was well known for gladiatorial events which usually pitted one or more beings against savage creatures from around the galaxy. Around 32 BBY, the ringmaster had a run in with Jedi Masters Mace Windu and Depa Billaba when an illegal smuggling ring of akk dogs was traced back to him.
